*rdoc-3.4 (08 Jan 2011)

  08 Jan 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rdoc-3.4.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  02 Jan 2011; Tobias Klausmann <klausman@gentoo.org> rdoc-2.5.11.ebuild:
  Keyworded on alpha, bug #332593

  31 Dec 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> rdoc-3.2.ebuild:
  Be explicit about the slots to avoid wrong edge cases, reported by
  Arfrever.

*rdoc-3.2 (30 Dec 2010)

  30 Dec 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rdoc-3.2.ebuild:
  Version bump: more bug fixes.

  28 Dec 2010; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> rdoc-3.0.1-r1.ebuild:
  Marked ~x64-solaris

*rdoc-3.0.1-r1 (28 Dec 2010)

  28 Dec 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rdoc-3.0.1-r1.ebuild,
  +files/rdoc-3.0.1-bin-require.patch:
  Fix include path for script, thanks for James le Cuirot for the patch.

  27 Dec 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> rdoc-2.5.11.ebuild:
  Drop ruby19 support to create a stable candidate.

*rdoc-3.0.1 (27 Dec 2010)

  27 Dec 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rdoc-3.0.1.ebuild:
  Version bump: major enhancements and bug fixing. Ruby 1.8.6 is no longer
  supported.

  27 Dec 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -rdoc-2.5.6.ebuild,
  -rdoc-2.5.9.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

  04 Dec 2010; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> rdoc-2.5.11.ebuild:
  Marked ~x{86,64}-macos

  25 Oct 2010; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> rdoc-2.5.11.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa (bug #337956).

  10 Sep 2010; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> rdoc-2.5.11.ebuild:
  Fix for Prefix, bug #336704

*rdoc-2.5.11 (24 Aug 2010)

  24 Aug 2010; Alex Legler <a3li@gentoo.org> +rdoc-2.5.11.ebuild:
  Version bump. Fixes tests wrt bug 330279. ruby19 patch is no longer
  needed.

  18 Aug 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> rdoc-2.5.6.ebuild,
  rdoc-2.5.9.ebuild:
  Stop using virtual/ruby-minitest, since it's now unbundled from 1.9 as
  well.

  08 Aug 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> rdoc-2.5.9.ebuild:
  Use less existent nonexistent directory, fixing bug 321059.

